abstract: Chevron Corp on Friday posted a fourth-quarter loss as the oil major booked an impairment charge of $10.4 billion related largely to a deepwater Gulf of Mexico project, shale gas assets in Appalachia and the Kitmat LNG project in Canada.
snippet: Chevron Corp on Friday posted a fourth-quarter loss as the oil major booked an impairment charge of $10.4 billion related largely to a deepwater Gulf of Mexico project, shale gas assets in Appalachia and the Kitmat LNG project in Canada.
lead_paragraph: (Reuters) - Chevron Corp on Friday posted a fourth-quarter loss as the oil major booked an impairment charge of $10.4 billion related largely to a deepwater Gulf of Mexico project, shale gas assets in Appalachia and the Kitmat LNG project in Canada.
headline_main: Chevron Swings to Quarterly Loss on $10.4 Bln Impairment Charge
headline_print_headline: Chevron Swings to Quarterly Loss on $10.4 Bln Impairment Charge

abstract: Some companies have warned that a coronavirus outbreak in China that has killed more than 250 people and infected thousands could disrupt supply chains or hurt bottom lines as factories and shops shut and airlines suspend flights.

abstract: Why are Roc Nation and the N.F.L. doing business this Super Bowl weekend? Well, social justice is expensive.
snippet: Why are Roc Nation and the N.F.L. doing business this Super Bowl weekend? Well, social justice is expensive.
lead_paragraph: A few years ago, the National Football League approached Jay-Z about performing at the Super Bowl halftime show. To perform “Run This Town,” he was asked if he would bring Rihanna and Kanye West, who appear on the track, along with him.

abstract: She became a world-renowned author writing about “nice people whose lives are invaded.”
snippet: She became a world-renowned author writing about “nice people whose lives are invaded.”
lead_paragraph: Mary Higgins Clark, a fixture on best-seller lists for decades whose more than 50 novels earned her the sobriquet Queen of Suspense, died on Friday in Naples, Fla. She was 92.

abstract: Mary Higgins Clark, the tireless and long-reigning "Queen of Suspense" whose tales of women beating the odds made her one of the world's most popular writers, died Friday at age 92.
snippet: Mary Higgins Clark, the tireless and long-reigning "Queen of Suspense" whose tales of women beating the odds made her one of the world's most popular writers, died Friday at age 92.
lead_paragraph: NEW YORK — Mary Higgins Clark, the tireless and long-reigning "Queen of Suspense" whose tales of women beating the odds made her one of the world's most popular writers, died Friday at age 92.
headline_main: Author Mary Higgins Clark,' Queen of Suspense,' Dead at 92
headline_print_headline: Author Mary Higgins Clark,' Queen of Suspense,' Dead at 92

abstract: Republican legislators abdicated their duty by refusing to seek the truth.
snippet: Republican legislators abdicated their duty by refusing to seek the truth.
lead_paragraph: Alas, no one ever lost money betting on the cynicism of today’s congressional Republicans. On Friday evening, Republican senators voted in near lock step to block testimony from any new witnesses or the production of any new documents, a vote that was tantamount to an acquittal of the impeachment charges against President Trump. The move can only embolden the president to cheat in the 2020 election.

abstract: The Sanders online army resembles President Trump’s most ardent supporters in more ways than either side might care to admit.
snippet: The Sanders online army resembles President Trump’s most ardent supporters in more ways than either side might care to admit.
lead_paragraph: Barbara Boxer minces no words when it comes to describing the people usually known as the Bernie Bros — a subset of Bernie Sanders supporters who hope to take over the Democratic Party and remake it in their image.

abstract: Three days before the Iowa caucuses begin the 2020 nominating process, Joe Biden’s campaign manager downplayed the significance of Iowa and New Hampshire and prepped supporters for an extended primary season.
snippet: Three days before the Iowa caucuses begin the 2020 nominating process, Joe Biden’s campaign manager downplayed the significance of Iowa and New Hampshire and prepped supporters for an extended primary season.
lead_paragraph: DES MOINES, Iowa — Three days before the Iowa caucuses begin the 2020 nominating process, Joe Biden’s campaign manager downplayed the significance of Iowa and New Hampshire and prepped supporters for an extended primary season.
headline_main: Biden Camp Prepping Backers for Extended Fight Beyond Iowa
headline_print_headline: Biden Camp Prepping Backers for Extended Fight Beyond Iowa
